lead_paragraph: Australian Scott Hend and Chile's Felipe Aguilar shot three-under-par 69s to lead the way in the Scottish Open after a windy first round at Castle Stuart on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Hend, Aguilar Set Pace at Windy Scottish Open
